<div class="article-teaser"><span style="white-space: nowrap;" class="key"></span></div><div class ="article-teaser">The properties of hydrogen and helium under extreme conditions   [Jeffrey M. McMahon, Miguel A. Morales, Carlo Pierleoni, and David M. Ceperley, <span class="journal">Rev. Mod. Phys.</span> <span class="volume" style="font-weight: bold;">84</span>, <span class="page">1607</span> (2012)<abbr class="issue" title="4"></abbr><abbr class="doi" title="10.1103/RevModPhys.84.1607"></abbr><abbr class="date-published" title="2012-11-13T00:00:00Z"></abbr>]</div>
